{"tid":2018201,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好似我26歲先打第一份工","createTime":"2020-05-15T12:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T09:29:40.000Z","uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a8c047f0eec6dfe299790a82beb2a74b8e96cb95","tid":2018201,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:59:45.000Z","msg":"17歲前渾渾噩噩，突然醒覺，覺得讀書學歷重要，於是由F.3讀起，到22歲先中學畢業，然後讀Diploma<br />\n<br />\n26歲突然覺得自己年紀都唔細，應該要出嚟返工，拿工作經驗，於是$8000一個月，做IT Support返五日半<br />\n<br />\n到28歲，讀完Top up野雞大學，轉公司<br />\n<br />\n今年37歲，有個野雞Degree，仍然做緊IT Support，每日返嚟公司裝下Windows 10，幫同事換下mouse，Solve下Outlook，Solve下network connection，吹一啲人地唔識，但IT人就覺得好易既野，日日就叫人restart電腦<br />\n<br />\n想移民，但就得個唸字！年紀大，學歷又差，英文又差！除左每月得幾萬蚊人工，真係覺得人生好無意義！唔想裝Windows，換Mouse幾十年"},{"pid":"8b9cf756539357df017e985e2259493b3716696a","tid":2018201,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"雞哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344622d91c9876a0ff8fe071f9084593644d2bc5","tid":2018201,"uid":343361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講漏咗Daddy 留比你啲50億遺産<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1f2bdb58c38116f5f9b1a455874849cd1f2a1c33","tid":2018201,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"344622d91c9876a0ff8fe071f9084593644d2bc5","tid":2018201,"uid":343361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講漏咗Daddy 留比你啲50億遺産<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67522c3b68ca2dbfb5c8ce980083fcafa0